Output docs/demo/demo.gif

Set Theme "Catppuccin Mocha"
Set FontSize 14
Set Width 700
Set Height 450
Set Shell "zsh"
Set Padding 16
Set TypingSpeed 80ms

Sleep 500ms

Type "huddy random"
Enter
Sleep 2s

Type "huddy random"
Enter
Sleep 2s

Type "huddy select cat"
Enter
Sleep 2s

Type "huddy info"
Enter
Sleep 2s

Type "sh docs/demo/demo-hud.sh"
Enter
Sleep 3s
